description: right profile portrait of long haired man wearing fur collared cloak, holding rolled paper in right hand; left hand on chest
inscription:
Title, and Inscription

on sheet in black [ALBERTUS DURERUS, NORE BERGENS/ Vir virtute gravis, trimque arte insigneo sabetur/ Teutonicae genlis gloria summa suce/ contulet suic Caesar insigna Nobilitatis/ Tantur sonas artis, famaque tanta viri]; in pencil on sheet: [1-369]
title: Portrait of Albertus Durerus, Norebergens
